cs.GT, cs.IR, cs.DS, cs.MA, cs.LG. 

The paper discusses the implementation of display advertising contracts through randomized bidding, which involves auction theory and game theory (cs.GT). It also involves the allocation of impressions based on value, which is related to information retrieval (cs.IR) and data structures (cs.DS). The concept of creating a mutual fund of advertising impressions may involve machine learning (cs.LG) and multi-agent systems (cs.MA).
